beer.beer_name: Electric Feel Cryo Hopped Oat Cream IPA
beer.beer_description: A smooth, soft IPA exuding sweet, juicy flavours. Tantalising hop aromas creates a buzz before the pop of citrus and stone fruit flavour from the cryo pop and citra hops, all smoothed over by the pillow soft texture from the oats.
